<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="quit-v">quit <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kwɪt/    美 /kwɪt/  </p>
<p>(quit / quitted, quit / quitted) vt &amp; vi [非正式用语]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>离开 (工作、学校等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>quit a job / quit school
辞职/辍学</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>停止；戒除：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He didn’t quit, and he became a great pianist.
他没有放弃，最终成为一名伟大的钢琴家。</p><footer>北师大② – 5</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>quit doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father has quit smoking at last.
我父亲终于戒了烟。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>关闭 / 退出 (计算机程序等)</strong></h4></div>